products.description: The Raceway Poncho is our iconic Western style poncho that features an all-over raceway knit in black & white and is finished with a 4inch tonal fringe. Our poncho's are perfect for layering or as a stand alone statement piece. A timeless, unisex classic that fits all. MATERIAL 28% Polyester 32% Acrylic 40% Nylon CARE INSTRUCTIONS Washing: To maintain the garments texture and pattern, hand wash gently in cold water with a mild detergent and avoid using harsh chemicals or fabric softeners. Drying: Ensure the sleeves are straight to maintain their shape and lay flat on a towel to air dry. To avoid tangling or damage to the fringe, gently comb through with your fingers while it is still damp. Avoid wringing or twisting as this may also cause the fringe to tangle. Avoid hanging the garment when drying to avoid stretching. *Following these steps will ensure the longevity and beauty of your iconic Western Poncho.
